    See how much energy and water we are using 
  </p>

      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row ">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
        <div id="contents" class="app-c-contents-list-with-body">
    
        <div class="responsive-bottom-margin">
          
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Information from our electricity, gas and water meters is transmitted at half-hour intervals to a central data capture point. You can see <a rel="external" href="http://www.ecodriver.uk.com/DFID/" title="How much energy and water we are using">charts of how much energy and water we are using</a>.</p>

<p>You can also download the raw data. Over time this data can be used to map long-term trends on performance.</p>

